# HireHub Onboarding Portal - Environment Variables
# ================================================
# This is a static SPA — no environment variables are required.
# All configuration is currently hardcoded.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development:
#   cp .env.example .env.local
#
# Vite exposes env vars prefixed with VITE_ to the client.
# Access them via import.meta.env.VITE_*
#
# ------------------------------------------------
# Future placeholders (uncomment and set as needed):
# ------------------------------------------------
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api
# VITE_APP_TITLE=HireHub Onboarding Portal
# VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=false